{"tid":1605534,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【連儂牆爭議】中大內地生嘲諷：「嫌功課不夠多？？」","createTime":"2019-09-30T10:14:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-30T12:31:32.000Z","uid":226548,"like":1,"dislike":20,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"289e2b304b2c3fcccd45d631e56753f84fed8830","tid":1605534,"uid":226548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T10:14:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/srfLXd6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsrfLXd6.jpg&h=eacbe5a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  中大生日前自發在校園貼上單張、噴漆宣揚反送中，將百萬大道化成連儂大道，校方其後發聲明表示，對於校園被損污感遺憾及痛心，指「不能以言論自由作為辯解」。有學生斥聲明「離譜」，稱校方在學生抗爭被捕時沒有伸手援助，對於不構成傷害人的行為卻出聲譴責，認為做法不合理。另有<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">內地生稱，學生的責任就是讀書，作為中國人亦理所當然要愛國</span></strong>。<br />\n<br />\n  商學院四年級內地生Shakie選擇的是留在同溫層，對這場運動不聞不問。在回答記者提問時，她一直帶有保留，「我不方便多說『民主』、『自由』這些東西，就保持自己的觀念&hellip;&hellip;對！我很愛國！」她又向記者反問，「<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你連自己的國家都不愛，那你還愛甚麼呢？</span></strong>」"},{"pid":"8a09e7321c7026b8eee3a5daf7b68c20abfb0e35","tid":1605534,"uid":222970,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T10:14:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"beceb9b823a1dfe7d52c975cf78f769da144e292","tid":1605534,"uid":226548,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-30T10:14:44.000Z","msg":"Source:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_697115_0?utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_campaign=hknext_article_share&amp;utm_content=share_link&amp;fbclid=IwAR11D8-4iSeKIgSWY7FrmQUUKqwEzN9S0fLe1kT6NC7L1eRIideTLwZDGdI\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Farticle%2F2_697115_0%3Futm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_campaign%3Dhknext_article_share%26utm_content%3Dshare_link%26fbclid%3DIwAR11D8-4iSeKIgSWY7FrmQUUKqwEzN9S0fLe1kT6NC7L1eRIideTLwZDGdI&d=l0hx0y7EoyLX%2BzZhnd86ZqjoMSgg1pB26AL%2BN7DPQls%3D&h=91399978\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextme